sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant UI as UI
  participant K as Kong
  participant PAY as Plan Payment
  participant SQL as SQL
  participant PG as Pay Gateway

  U->>UI: Buy plan
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/orders JWT
  K->>PAY: forward
  PAY->>SQL: order PENDING
  PAY->>PG: create session
  PG-->>PAY: pay URL
  PAY-->>UI: orderId + checkout

  Note over U,PG: User pays on provider site

  PG->>K: POST /webhooks/payment signed
  K->>PAY: verify
  PAY->>SQL: order PAID payment row
  PAY-->>PG: 200 OK
